# Naming Conventions

## File Naming

- **General files**: Use lowercase_underscore format (e.g., `recent_7days_issues.json`)
- **Summary files**: Use format `{TICKET_KEY}_{desc}.md` (e.g., `PROJ-123_feature_analysis.md`)
- **JSON files**: Use format `{desc}_{timeframe}.json` (e.g., `issues_last_week.json`)

## Examples

- ✅ `recent_7days_issues.json`
- ✅ `PROJ-456_user_feedback.md`
- ✅ `sprint_data_q1_2024.json`
- ❌ `Recent7DaysIssues.json` (wrong format)
- ❌ `proj-123.md` (missing description)
